name: StoryBots: Answer Time
overview: Got a question? The StoryBots have an answer! Join curious friends Beep, Boop, Bing, Bang and Bo on fun adventures to find facts for real kids like you.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: The 'Bots are back to answer more curious questions from kids like you, like how do bubbles form? Why does the moon change shape? And how is glass made?

episodes.name: Multiplication
episodes.overview: Something's not adding up for Giuseppe the pizza guy, but Beep totally knows how to help â€” multiplication! Danny DeVito guest-stars.

episodes.name: Keys
episodes.overview: When a cat burglar has a question about keys, Boop goes to Security Hardware Headquarters to unlock the answer. Zooey Deschanel guest-stars.

episodes.name: Glue
episodes.overview: How does glue work? Mr. Wonderful can't start his show until Bang gets to the bottom of this sticky question. Common guest-stars.

episodes.name: Sand
episodes.overview: To build a sandcastle, a royal architect wants to know where sand comes from. It's up to Bo to get to the nitty gritty. Sophie Turner guest-stars.

episodes.name: Budgets
episodes.overview: Mr. Awesome Ultra Guy is curious about budgets, so Bing pays a visit to the bank. Kevin Smith guest-stars.

episodes.name: Lasers
episodes.overview: When a secret agent asks the StoryBots about lasers, Bang shoots the question to a photon named Frans. Anne Hathaway guest-stars.

episodes.name: Taste
episodes.overview: Ms. Mushroom wants to learn how to taste better. To find out more, Bo goes to see her favorite band, the Taste Buds. Chrissy Teigen guest-stars.

episodes.name: Ice
episodes.overview: Boop visits the Chemical Department to answer a burning question for Mr. Super Snowy Icy Cone Guy: How is ice made? Patton Oswalt guest-stars.

episodes.name: Dizzy
episodes.overview: Bing takes a spin to the Department of Bodily Functions to help Mr. Karate Guy understand why people get dizzy. Gabriel Iglesias guest-stars.

episodes.name: GPS
episodes.overview: A lost tourist wants to know how GPS works, so Beep travels to Old Willy's map to learn more. Craig Robinson guest-stars.

episodes.name: Fractions
episodes.overview: Cosmic Caller thinks he found an alien code, but something's not adding up. Bing talks to Alabama Smith to figure things out. Rainn Wilson guest-stars.

episodes.name: Bubbles
episodes.overview: Before his big show, the Great Bubblini is bursting to know how bubbles form. Bang heads to the laundromat to find out. Josh Gad guest-stars.

episodes.name: Area
episodes.overview: When Disco Delilah asks how many tiles she'll need for her dance floor, Beep steps up to learn more about area. Wendi McLendon-Covey guest-stars.

episodes.name: Moon
episodes.overview: Bo explores why the moon seems to change shape to help Ms. Astronaut Lady safely land her spaceship. Scarlett Johansson guest-stars.

episodes.name: Taxes
episodes.overview: Ms. Firefighter has a burning question about taxes, so Boop visits the Department of Government and Stuff. Gabrielle Union guest-stars.

episodes.name: Tornados
episodes.overview: Beep takes a spin with documentarian Chase Weathers to answer Mr. Cow's question about how tornadoes form. Joe Lo Truglio guest-stars.

episodes.name: Glass
episodes.overview: Where does glass come from? Mr. Castaway can't make windows for his house until Bo cracks this question. Steve Buscemi guest-stars.

episodes.name: Refrigerator
episodes.overview: After Ms. Cafeteria Worker Lady's refrigerator stops working, Bing visits the Refrigadome to learn more about cooling. Kristen Bell guest-stars.

episodes.name: Elements
episodes.overview: Boop travels to the Archive Department to help the all-knowing Socradamus with a fundamental question: What is stuff made of? Simu Liu guest-stars.

episodes.name: Stocks
episodes.overview: When Ms. Clown gets an offer to invest in e-Digital-Clown-Circus-World.com, Bang pays a visit to a TV show about stocks. Julie Bowen guest-stars.

episodes.name: Internet
episodes.overview: Bo looks into how the internet works after an office worker named Stacy accidentally sends a silly video to his boss. Trevor Noah guest-stars.

episodes.name: Time and Distance
episodes.overview: Bing races to ask runner Speedy Lightning a question about finding the fastest route for Ms. Pizza Delivery Lady. Jessica Alba guest-stars.
